ple.com\">Manage Users</a> module and making the appropriate changes. </p><p>To learn more about user roles in iTunes Connect, view the Manage Users section of the <a href=\"http://itunesconnect.apple.com/docs/iTunesConnect_DeveloperGuide.pdf\">iTunes Connect Developer Guide</a>. </p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:89;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"\n\n\n\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:4:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Apple Developer Forums Offer New Features\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"http://developer.apple.com/news/index.php?id=03252010a\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:318:\"New features and functionality have been added to the Apple Developer Forums. The Forums now feature improved performance for faster browsing and a new rating system that makes it easier to find the answers that other developers find most helpful. Log in to the Apple Developer Forums and start your discussions today.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Thu, 25 Mar 2010 13:47:41 PDT\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:501:\"\n<p>New features and functionality have been added to the Apple Developer Forums. The Forums now feature improved performance for faster browsing and a new rating system that makes it easier to find the answers that other developer